	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				世界那么大，logo 们也想静静。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p class="MsoNormal">
	有人把耐克的&nbsp;<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">slogan&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">从“</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Just&nbsp;Do&nbsp;It</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">”画成了“</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Just&nbsp;Do&nbsp;Not</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">”发布在推特上引发众人围观。</span><o:p></o:p>
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/d4c8136edda5.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	这位插画家名叫库尔茨（<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Adam&nbsp;J.&nbsp;Kurtz</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">），</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">在玩坏了耐克的&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">之后，他在几个小时之内又陆续发出了其他品牌&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的悲伤时刻，你会看见可口可乐、星巴克等众多&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">一起组成“世界上最悲伤的&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">们”。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	“真诚是人们最为立体有趣的情感，把一些悲伤的元素加入品牌&nbsp;<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">中或许会很有意思”，库尔茨对&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.adweek.com/">Adweek</a>&nbsp;表示。作为&nbsp;<a href="http://yrbff.tumblr.com/">BuzzFeed&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">公司&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">BFF</span></a>&nbsp;创意团队的一员，他热爱新颖有趣的创意。在他看来，品牌&nbsp;<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">logo&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">不应该是大众在社交平台上秀日常的一个“植入”，尽管人们在社交平台中光鲜亮丽，但更多时候心里是有一些负能量的，现在他希望用一种更为幽默的方式表达出来。</span><o:p></o:p>
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	他还在<a href="https://twitter.com/ADAMJK">推特</a>上说，如果同时有两件耐克的&nbsp;<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">T&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">恤摆在他的面前，一件写着“</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Just&nbsp;Do&nbsp;It</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">”，一件写着“</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Just&nbsp;Do&nbsp;Not</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">”，他会选择后者。</span><o:p></o:p>
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;">下面我们来看看这些 logo：</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/0b7a91737841.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">百加得（<span style="white-space:normal;">BACARDI</span>）：变成了“</span><span style="white-space:normal;">BACARDOT”。</span></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/04ffed9d873e.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#333333;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;text-indent:28px;white-space:normal;">露诗 (LUSH)：我</span>快要尖叫出来了，你能听见我的声音吗？<br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/49a85be37503.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;">企鹅：救救我，为了保持我 1935 年来的领导地位，我脖子都抽筋了。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/8f6757965ed8.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	可口可乐：喝了这饮料，所有的破事都来了。<img src="/uploads/image/201505/37bc318fb9d5.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">蓝带</span><span style="color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">啤酒</span><span style="color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">(Pabst Blue Ribbon)：噢</span>，然而它还只是一杯啤酒。
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201505/0915966c43f3.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="color:#CC0000;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">Chipotle&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#333333;font-family:arial;font-size:13px;line-height:20.020000457763672px;white-space:normal;">快餐店：难吃到死。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201505/35b06595b566.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	星巴克：不许拍照。
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201505/857d578c1804.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	宜家：<span style="color:#3F3F3F;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;">家具特么要你自己装！</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	特别说明：非官方翻译，各位请随意
</p>
		</div>
